Linus shares a big win for consumer-friendly NAS setups: Eshtek, the company he invested in, is sponsoring a major ZFS update that finally enables efficient mixed-drive pools. With “Any RAID” support, users will soon be able to get more usable storage from mismatched drives, something the enterprise-focused ZFS has long lacked. Linus and Luke discuss.
